{"tid":680883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭 芳 芳 落 舖 撐 GiGi 老 公","createTime":"2018-05-27T13:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T14:13:01.000Z","uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24880e775ceeaf941991cab8aee30a25c195e39d","tid":680883,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:58:21.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）的西班牙籍老公Sergio最近在香港開設童裝限定店，身為太太的GiGi當然支持，除了現身限定店做生招牌外，更不扣除成本將總收入的20%撥捐「護苗基金」。<br />\n<br />\n護苗基金會長蕭芳芳日前親自去店舖，Sergio見到對方突擊到訪感到開心，芳芳姐還用流利的西班牙文和Sergio溝通，又自掏腰包買童裝送給親友，Sergio說：「芳芳姐非常親切，優雅又幽默風趣，難怪我太太事事以芳芳姐為榜樣，芳芳姐是她最尊敬和仰慕的前輩。」GiGi當日因要照顧囡囡未有現身，她笑說：「我居然錯過咗，我都好想帶囡囡見媽咪嘅偶像。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24ec2p2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24ec2p2e.jpg&h=003e35fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b3cd06dabf2e33bbcef44d7d62d648d84d5bd5c","tid":680883,"uid":94501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span>"},{"pid":"dfe8c7e8d2529ca85d719440782758240bb245b0","tid":680883,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"煩到閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf307266c5866d4066f2a6095e468ee1f368e6d","tid":680883,"uid":33147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3cd06dabf2e33bbcef44d7d62d648d84d5bd5c","tid":680883,"uid":94501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班</span></span>"}]}